{"tid":1763431,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"首先推左聽日行動Post先，聽日過後再傾2020普選，咩白票各有各做","createTime":"2019-11-30T10:27:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T12:31:59.000Z","uid":110109,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f6e107e7b0e99b547c0a02ccb2aa3ec52bb09d62","tid":1763431,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T10:27:53.000Z","msg":"聽日最早可以十點<br />\n然後中環十二點 直落<br />\n尖沙嘴 三點呀！！！<br />\n<br />\n行動最緊要，聽日再傾2020應該做啲咩<br />\n<br />\n今日興嘈白票<br />\n但係第一樣嘢首先我地要諗既係<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>記得五大訴求係乜嘢嗎</strong></span><br />\n遊行前再諗一次五大訴求係咩<br />\n<br />\n雙普選，特首普選可能遠左啲<br />\n但係2020立法會普選，團結的話絕對有得爭取<br />\n假如我地一派仲跟港共個套循序漸進理論<br />\n玩功能組別、玩特首選委<br />\n咁係唔係自我瓦解左自己既真普選訴求？<br />\n咁又算唔算係血債票償？<br />\n手足坐多1+4年，快則2024，我地終於贏到立法會再開始平反？五年後先拎到權返黎查梓樂、彥霖單案？<br />\n<br />\n自己嘗試判斷"},{"pid":"9fdb8b5c81283cb56bcd9fe23fd62ce271de6f1b","tid":1763431,"uid":175159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T10:29:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ao01uLY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fao01uLY.jpg&h=f28d2116&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6QAs9LY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6QAs9LY.jpg&h=f8992b4f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RyxjgqZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRyxjgqZ.jpg&h=2e82d3a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ffa27347397fe4e8aac8db54d60042d0af3d18c9","tid":1763431,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T10:30:02.000Z","msg":"我地唔可以沉醉喺區選勝利入面<br />\n呢個制度係一個萬劫不復既陷阱黎<br />\n我地好辛苦爬左一半就到洞口<br />\n係，共產黨真係冇咁簡單就會放你走。<br />\n<br />\n咁但係我地真係要再跌返落去？"},{"pid":"ca721b8c99cd46c304ac6400cd07ee51f9e6a998","tid":1763431,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fdb8b5c81283cb56bcd9fe23fd62ce271de6f1b","tid":1763431,"uid":175159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-3